### **Context-Aware Translation**

```bash
aii translate "running late for meeting" to spanish

# ğŸ§  Converting informal business expression, maintaining urgency...
# ğŸŒ "Voy a llegar tarde a la reuniÃ³n"
# ğŸ“ Informal but professional. Alternative: "Me voy a retrasar" (more formal)
